item.summary: login page not loaded correctly in openid-jc sample

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.

comments.comment:
I have created a pull request
https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-security/pull/84

Thanks for the bug submission and the PR. We actually don't want to remove the configuration. Instead, we were missing the login page that should have been displayed. This was happening because samples was mistakenly added to .gitignore.

Please try updating and running the application. You should now see the custom openid login page.
This issue has been migrated to https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-security/issues/2772
